{"type": "article", "id": 14903, "title": "Topstitch鞋", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-15T07:10:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000314PE2vF3bwiyfxANIT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tBalenciaga（巴黎世家）推出了秋冬系列 Topstitch，灵感来自于徒步靴。黑色或白色的小牛皮通过饰钉固定，以搭配出简洁硬朗的风格。粗线条的橡胶鞋底，让这款鞋看上去非常结实，适合走中性风的女生。其中白色牛皮配黑底的鞋在色彩上构成强烈的对比，在粗狂中有一份优雅，很有吸引力。高帮款侧面带有黑色松紧带，低帮正面系鞋带。<a href=\"http://www.balenciaga.cn/cn/topstitch-%E9%9E%8B%E5%B1%A5_cod44907520ng.html\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142315UNVBOfD0EJRAegc3.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142315rUqanuZG4zOMSYgv.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142316ED26nMoTNYrWXtR7.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142316b1c0xFkLtvEQTJdS.jpg\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}